    title: "Benefits of Piling Foundations in Construction Projects",
    description: "Learn the practical and structural advantages of piling foundations, including durability, lateral resistance, and suitability for difficult soil profiles.",
    author: "Dwizzy Infra Team",
    date: "2026-05-21",
    category: "Infrastructure",
    readTime: "6 min read",
    image: BlogImg,
    keywords: [
        "benefits of piling foundations",
        "pile foundations",
        "construction projects",
        "deep foundations",
        "heavy civil construction",
        "Dwizzy Infra",
